To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [(unofficial) choco:// Protocol support ](https://chocolatey.org/packages/choco-protocol-support)

## NOTE: Actual driver version 1909.12.0.1236

## Detailed Description

Intel® Management Engine Driver for Windows 8.1* and Windows® 10 supporting

* 6th Generation Intel® Core™ Processor Family (Sky Lake)
* 7th Generation Intel® Core™ Processor Family (Kaby Lake)
* 8th Generation Intel® Core™ Processor Family (Kaby Lake R)

### INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS:
There is a **Consumer** and a **Corporate** version of these drivers. You can specify which version to install using package parameters, examples are below. Not specifying a version will default to the Consumer drivers.

### INSTALL EXAMPLES:
* choco install intel-me-drivers --params "'/TYPE:consumer'" (default)
* choco install intel-me-drivers --params "'/TYPE:corporate'"

**[PACKAGE NOTES](https://github.com/bcurran3/ChocolateyPackages/blob/master/intel-me-drivers/readme.md)**
